  # this data should be stored by boss?  architect? probably boss
  # should know what the various pieces of code do.  its part of the
  # data for capabilities mapping, mapping tasks to code right there
  # is room for improvement.  by knowing what functions are being
  # editted, and what capabilities those functions provide, we can
  # instantly know what the task context is.  A task subsumption
  # hierarchy can then be used to view time-in-task and productivity
  # in any context by any programmer

